.el .ds Aq '
.TH grex-teardown 1  "grex-teardown " 
.SH NAME
grex\-teardown \- Tear down a pack tree (reverse of `sync`/`install`)
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBgrex\-teardown\fR [\fB\-\-workspace\fR] [\fB\-q\fR|\fB\-\-quiet\fR] [\fB\-\-no\-validate\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] [\fIPACK_ROOT\fR] 
.SH DESCRIPTION
Tear down a pack tree (reverse of `sync`/`install`)
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-workspace\fR=\fIWORKSPACE\fR
Workspace directory. Defaults to `<pack_root>/.grex/workspace`
.TP
\fB\-q\fR, \fB\-\-quiet\fR
Suppress per\-action log lines
.TP
\fB\-\-no\-validate\fR
Skip plan\-phase validators. Debug\-only escape hatch
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.TP
[\fIPACK_ROOT\fR]
Pack root. Directory holding `.grex/pack.yaml`, or the YAML file itself. When omitted, `teardown` prints a usage stub and exits 0
